code.value:
from axiestudio import CustomComponent

from langchain.llms.base import BaseLLM
from langchain.chains import LLMChain
from langchain import PromptTemplate
from langchain.schema import Document
from langchain.document_loaders import WebBaseLoader

import requests

class YourComponent(CustomComponent):
    display_name: str = "Batch WebLoader"
    description: str = "Run WebBaseLoader on multiple urls."

    def build_config(self):
        return { "urls": { "multiline": True, "required": True} }

    def build(self, urls: str, chain: LLMChain, truncate: int=5000) -> Document:
        urls = eval(urls)
        results = []
        for url in urls:
            document = WebBaseLoader(url).load()[0]
            result = chain.run({"webpage": document.page_content[:int(truncate)]})
            results.append(result)
        self.repr_value = results
        return results
